OL,3,CLondon Eye breaks down, leaving
OL,4,Cpassengers stuck 135 metres in the air
OL,6,FThe London Eye was brought to a
OL,7,Fstandstill today as it broke down on
OL,8,Fwhat's been the hottest day of the
OL,9,Fyear so far.
OL,11,FEarlier a technical issue meant the
OL,12,Ficonic tourist attraction stopped,
OL,13,Fwhile passengers were still onboard
OL,14,Fthe 135m attraction.
OL,16,FIt left queues waiting on the South
OL,17,FBank, as temperatures surged towards
OL,18,F28C.
