OL,3,CLondon Eye breaks down, leaving
OL,4,Cpassengers stuck 135 metres in the air
OL,6,FThe London Eye X account confirmed it
OL,7,Fis now back up and running.
OL,9,FA post read: "Earlier today, the
OL,10,FLondon Eye temporarily paused to
OL,11,Finvestigate a minor technical issue.
OL,13,F"Our team were able to quickly resolve
OL,14,Fthe issue, resulting in a short 10
OL,15,Fminute delay to boarding, after which
OL,16,Fwe resumed operating as usual.
OL,18,F"We apologise for any inconvenience
OL,19,Fcaused."
